## Core type groups

| Group | Key types |
| --- | --- |
| Uniforms | `UniformType`, `UniformValue`, `UniformMap`, `UniformLayout` |
| Textures | `TextureValue`, `TextureDefinition`, `TextureMap`, `TextureUpdateMode` |
| Passes | `RenderPass`, `RenderPassContext`, `RenderTargetDefinitionMap` |
| Scheduler | `RenderMode`, `FrameState`, `FrameInvalidationToken`, `FrameRunTimings` |
| Diagnostics | `MotionGPUErrorReport`, `MotionGPUErrorPhase` |
